Class PreparedStatementDecorator

java.lang.Object
  at.fpmedv.jdbc.PreparedStatementDecorator
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.sql.PreparedStatement, java.sql.Statement, java.sql.Wrapper
public abstract class PreparedStatementDecorator
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.sql.PreparedStatement

PreparedStatementDecorator class wraps around an existing PreparedStatement implementation and all calls are made against the underlying Object. Following the decorator pattern you can add extra functionality by extending this abstract class.

Author:
Franz Philipp Moser
See Also:
PreparedStatement
